00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:10.280
So the basic aspects of these
things you probably know.

00:14:12.860 --> 00:14:18.770
The best ones really depend
on knowing your location.

00:14:18.770 --> 00:14:23.030
So again, you have to
give the app permission

00:14:23.030 --> 00:14:26.660
to know your location
through your smartphone.

00:14:26.660 --> 00:14:29.600
If you don't do that, they
don't work well at all.

00:14:29.600 --> 00:14:31.370
Because, basically,
then you have

00:14:31.370 --> 00:14:33.560
to tell them where you are.

00:14:33.560 --> 00:14:39.640
And most of them don't even
have a good way to do that.

00:14:39.640 --> 00:14:44.600
The NextBus one, which
was the earliest one,

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.730
does have a drop-down
menu, if you don't want

00:14:46.730 --> 00:14:48.050
to tell them your location.

00:14:48.050 --> 00:14:52.650
And you can just
pick as you go down.

00:14:52.650 --> 00:14:55.030
But the other ones
don't really offer that.

00:14:55.030 --> 00:14:57.140
You basically have to
tell them the location.

00:14:57.140 --> 00:14:58.740
And it works well.

00:14:58.740 --> 00:15:00.500
It knows where you
are right away.

00:15:00.500 --> 00:15:02.530
It looks at
everything around you

00:15:02.530 --> 00:15:05.000
and it gives you the schedules,
the next couple buses

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:08.100
that are right around you.

00:15:08.100 --> 00:15:11.780
And so you can download
any of these things

00:15:11.780 --> 00:15:13.790
and see how it works.

00:15:13.790 --> 00:15:16.640
I go between
NextBus and Transit.

00:15:16.640 --> 00:15:18.260
I haven't used
CityMapper that much.

00:15:18.260 --> 00:15:20.360
Although in Europe,
almost everyone

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:25.340
uses CityMapper much more
than any of these other ones.

00:15:28.410 --> 00:15:32.570
The newest thing has been
providing these other modes.

00:15:32.570 --> 00:15:38.330
So essentially on Transit
now, you can order an Uber.

00:15:38.330 --> 00:15:45.500
And you could look at anyone
who wants to give them

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:48.900
data, essentially, of options.

