PROFESSOR: They can push.

01:00:43.750 --> 01:00:44.250
Yeah.

01:00:44.250 --> 01:00:45.964
AUDIENCE: Take
pictures [INAUDIBLE]

01:00:45.964 --> 01:00:46.630
PROFESSOR: Yeah.

