I think a lot of people do that.

01:00:48.040 --> 01:00:48.850
Yeah.

01:00:48.850 --> 01:00:51.550
I think London does
the same thing.

01:00:51.550 --> 01:00:53.280
London has a lot of these.

01:00:53.280 --> 01:00:54.406
And they--

01:00:54.406 --> 01:00:56.114
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Bus lanes and there

